name: DDicon_lora
description:
结合https://civitai.com/models/38511?modelVersionId=44457 的DDicon模型使用，生成玻璃质感web风格B端元素。

v1和v2版本建议对应使用，v1版本细节丰富复杂，v2版本细节简化，请按需使用。

Use the DDicon model from https://civitai.com/models/38511?modelVersionId=44457 to generate glass-like web-style B2B elements.

The v1 and v2 versions of the DDicon model are recommended to be used in conjunction, with the v1 version having detailed and complex settings, and the v2 version having simplified settings. Please use the model according to your needs.

Details are simplified to produce elements with a clear and concise structure.
